<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Login pannello EverGreen</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/hub.css" />
</head>

<body class="hub-login">
    <div class="hub-login-card">
        <div class="hub-login-brand">
            <img src="/assets/evergreen-logo.png" alt="EverGreen logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            <div>
                <div class="hub-login-eyebrow">EverGreen Competitive Hub</div>
                <h1>Accesso admin</h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>
            Questo pannello gira sempre sul web Northflank del bot. Da qui gestisci presenze reali, calendario e roster
            del team con la nuova interfaccia hub.
        </p>

        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="hub-flash error"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="post" action="/login">
            <label class="hub-label" for="token">Token admin</label>
            <input id="token" class="hub-input" type="password" name="token" placeholder="Inserisci il token admin" required />
            <button class="hub-button" type="submit" style="margin-top: 14px;">Accedi al pannello</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
